OL,3,CTop cleric leaves role claiming Church
OL,4,C'perpetuates bias and discrimination'
OL,6,FThe Rector at one of Liverpool's
OL,7,Foldest churches has claimed he cannot
OL,8,Fcontinue to work "in an organisation
OL,9,Fwhich perpetuates bias and
OL,10,Fdiscrimination against sections of
OL,11,Fsociety".
OL,13,FThe Revd Canon Dr Crispin Pailing,
OL,14,Fannounced on Sunday morning he was
OL,15,Fleaving his post at Liverpool Parish
OL,16,FChurch, after seeing the
OL,17,F"institutional validation of
OL,18,Fhomophobic and misogynistic views in
OL,19,Fthe Church".
