OL,6,FHe also used his resignation letter to
OL,7,Faddress what he called the "obvious
OL,8,Fand lamentable failure of safeguarding
OL,9,Facross the church" calling it an
OL,10,F"abuse in itself".
OL,12,FDr Pailing paid tribute to individuals
OL,13,Fwithin the church however, stating
OL,14,Fthat "in contrast to the institutional
OL,15,Factions which show such disregard for
OL,16,Fso many human beings" the majority
OL,17,Fspeak with "the voice of inclusion"
