OL,3,CTop cleric leaves role claiming Church
OL,4,C'perpetuates bias and discrimination'
OL,6,F"I am proud that Liverpool Parish
OL,7,FChurch continues to make a public
OL,8,Fdeclaration of the dignity of all
OL,9,Fpeople, in the knowledge that we are
OL,10,Fall made in God's image," he added.
OL,12,FThe cleric, who was awarded an MBE for
OL,13,Fservices to the community in December
OL,14,F2023 and whose job involves one of the
OL,15,Fmost significant civic roles in the
OL,16,Fcountry, says he will stand down in
OL,17,Fthe summer for a new role in the
OL,18,Fcharity sector.
OL,20,FITV Granada Reports has contacted the
OL,21,FChurch of England for comment.
