OL,6,FThe full statement from the Revd Canon
OL,7,FDr Crispin Pailing MBE
OL,9,F"After ten wonderful years as Rector
OL,10,Fof Liverpool, I announced this morning
OL,11,Fthat I shall be leaving this summer to
OL,12,Ftake up a new role in the charity
OL,13,Fsector.
OL,15,F"I cannot encapsulate in just a few
OL,16,Fwords how much I have enjoyed being at
OL,17,FLiverpool Parish Church, or the amount
OL,18,Fwhich we have achieved together.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/10
