OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F393A1711362802
OL,3,CTop cleric leaves role claiming Church
OL,4,C'perpetuates bias and discrimination'
OL,6,F"Liverpool Parish Church has one of
OL,7,Fthe most significant civic roles in
OL,8,Fthe country, and during the last few
OL,9,Fyears the congregation has changed and
OL,10,Fgrown in every way.
OL,12,F"During our time here my family has
OL,13,Fput down roots, and we wish to stay in
OL,14,Fthe city which has adopted us.
OL,16,F"Whilst I shall not get in the way of
OL,17,Fmy successor, I am so pleased that we
OL,18,Fshall still be able to call Liverpool
OL,19,Four home.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/10
