CT,2,C
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F393A1711362802
OL,3,CTop cleric leaves role claiming Church
OL,4,C'perpetuates bias and discrimination'
OL,6,F"You will gather from this that I
OL,7,Fshall not be working in the Church in
OL,8,Fthe future.
OL,10,F"I want to be clear about why this is.
OL,11,FI cannot, in good conscience, continue
OL,12,Fto have a representative role in an
OL,13,Forganisation which perpetuates bias
OL,14,Fand discrimination against sections of
OL,15,Fsociety on the grounds of sexuality,
OL,16,Frace, and gender.
OL,18,F"In the last few years I have seen the
OL,19,Finstitutional validation of homophobic
OL,20,Fand misogynistic views in the Church,
OL,21,Fand I cannot endorse this.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/10
