OL,3,CTop cleric leaves role claiming Church
OL,4,C'perpetuates bias and discrimination'
OL,6,F"The obvious and lamentable failure of
OL,7,Fsafeguarding across the church is
OL,8,Fitself an abuse, and a further assault
OL,9,Fon the image of God.
OL,11,F"In contrast to the institutional
OL,12,Factions which show such disregard for
OL,13,Fso many human beings, it seems to me
OL,14,Fthat the majority of individuals and
OL,15,Fcommunities across the Church of
OL,16,FEngland speak with the voice of
OL,17,Finclusion.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
