OL,4,C'perpetuates bias and discrimination'
OL,6,F"Paul Bayes and John Perumbalath have
OL,7,Fboth taken a significant public stance
OL,8,Fagainst the discrimination which many
OL,9,Fexperience.
OL,11,F"The Diocese of Liverpool has been a
OL,12,Fgood place to be for the last decade,
OL,13,Fand I commend it to others.
OL,15,F"Details of my final Sunday will of
OL,16,Fcourse be shared when they have been
OL,17,Fconfirmed, but for now there is still
OL,18,Fmuch for us to do together to proclaim
OL,19,Fthe Gospel of Jesus Christ in the
OL,20,Fcentre of our city: a Gospel of faith
OL,21,Fand hope and love.
